    GeneMANIA Nodes Example

    ex.gm.nodes.Rd

    Dataframe from GeneMANIA relating GeneMANIA IDs to common gene names.

    ex.gm.nodes

    Format

    Dataframe of 2762 rows and 16 columns:

    ...

    Source

    https://apps.cytoscape.org/apps/genemania

    Examples

    data(ex.gm.nodes)
